# Question 1: Password Validation

## Code

```python
# Question 1: Password Validation

passwords = input("Enter comma separated passwords: ").split(",")

valid_passwords = []

for p in passwords:
    p = p.strip()

    has_lower = False
    has_upper = False
    has_digit = False
    has_special = False

    for ch in p:
        if ch.islower():
            has_lower = True
        elif ch.isupper():
            has_upper = True
        elif ch.isdigit():
            has_digit = True
        elif ch in "$#@":
            has_special = True

    if 6 <= len(p) <= 12 and has_lower and has_upper and has_digit and has_special:
        valid_passwords.append(p)

print("Valid passwords:", ",".join(valid_passwords))
```

