# Question 2: Sort Tuples by Name, Age, Height

## Code

```python
# Question 2: Sort (name, age, height)

records = []

n = int(input("Enter number of records: "))

for i in range(n):
    print(f"Enter details for record {i+1}:")
    name = input("Name: ")
    age = input("Age: ")
    height = input("Height: ")
    records.append((name, age, height))

records.sort(key=lambda x: (x[0], x[1], x[2]))

print("Sorted list:")
print(records)
```

