```

### Calculation

* HRA = 20% of 20000 = 4000
* DA = 10% of 20000 = 2000
* Gross Salary = 20000 + 4000 + 2000 = 26000
* Tax = 5% of 26000 = 1300
* Net Salary = 26000 - 1300 = 24700

